caption: (Translated by Google) I ordered a roast beef and they sent me chicken and I had no way to communicate because I asked for it by Uber and also the food arrives cold.  (Original) Pedí una carne asada y me mandaron pollo y no tuve forma de comunicarme porque lo pedí por Uber y además la comida llega fría..
A must go to spot. New place , great authentic food. Good prices.
